504
00:24:55,410 --> 00:24:56,680
Of course. Heh.

505
00:24:56,680 --> 00:25:00,780
You and your siblings
are mighty indeed,

506
00:25:00,780 --> 00:25:02,040
yet the attacks on you
do show that you

507
00:25:02,050 --> 00:25:04,690
are not completely invulnerable.

508
00:25:04,690 --> 00:25:07,160
While you've wallowed
in your family affairs,

509
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:12,090
your progeny have grown
somewhat restless.

510
00:25:12,090 --> 00:25:15,420
The world is
a finite place,
territory limited,

511
00:25:15,430 --> 00:25:17,070
